{
  "id": "adv_main_01_07_02",
  "title": "星見編2章22話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_way-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（芽衣は無事すずと合流して寮に向かっているらしい）\n（どうやら二人の方が先に寮に着きそうだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mei managed to catch up to Suzu‚ and she’s taking her back to the dorm right now.)\n(It seems they’ll get back to the dorms before the rest of us.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 7.333333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "すずを強引に連れ去ろうとしてたから驚いたけど\n……お母さん、悪い人じゃなかったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She scared me at first because she was trying to take Suzu away‚\nbut Suzu’s mom… didn’t seem like a bad person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.173666628201804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "見た目も性格も、すずちゃんに似てたね\nそれに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ she looked and acted just like Suzu.\nNot to mention…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.20666659673056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ……もう。それは言ったら失礼よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Oh‚ dear. Don’t say anymore. That’s rude.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.761709444073677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "ゴチン、って結構いい音したけど\n大丈夫だったのかなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was a pretty epic clunk.\nI hope she’s okay…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.007990606971426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（そういえば……すずの母親は、去り際）\n（車に乗りこもうとしてしたたかに頭を打ちつけたな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(That’s right… when Suzu’s mother was leaving‚)\n(she hit her head on the car door when she was getting inside.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.34132394030476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "あ……同じタイミングだったみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… looks like we got back at the same time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 41.57465727363809
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 41.57465727363809
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 41.90799060697144
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "う……みなさん……\nさっきは……その……ええっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ girls!\nAbout what happened earlier‚ um…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1746572736381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 47.21581359738886
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "……そ、そうですわ！\nお、お母様はどうしたんですの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that’s right!\nW-where did my mother go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.74914693072223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今日のところはお引き取りいただいた\nただし、話し合いの場は必ず設ける、って条件付きだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had her pull back for today.\nBut on one condition: that you promise to talk to her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.94914693072223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 58.50399003315409
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "話し合い！？\n冗談じゃありませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talk to her?!\nDon’t be so ludicrous!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8706566998208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "話し合いなどしても\nあの方達が納得するはずありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No amount of talking it over\nwould get my parents to understand!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.17065669982079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 65.8039900331541
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すず、保護者の同意は絶対に必要だ\n自分で説得して、納得してもらわないと――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ you need your legal guardian’s permission.\nYou have to explain your case to them and get them to understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.97065669982078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 72.84415317006481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "私には一人でやっていくだけの力が充分にありますの！\nもう親の保護が必要な子供ではありませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I have more than enough strength to make it on my own!\nI am not a little child! I don’t need my parents’ permission for anything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.34415317006481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 80.47748650339813
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、すずはまだ中学三年生だろ\nそんな訳には――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Suzu‚ you’re still just a senior in middle school.\nI can’t just let you—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3108198367315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "失礼しますわ！！\nフン！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me!\nHumph!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.06846178797457,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 766.6666666666799,
          "startTime": 87.63512845464123
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 89.46846178797456
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "また逃げた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She ran away again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.46846178797456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 91.13512845464122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "今度は寮の中だから安心だけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time‚ she’s in the dorms‚ so I feel more at ease‚ but still…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.13512845464122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "私達にまであんな頑固な態度をとるなんて\n……ちょっと心配ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t believe she would be so stubborn‚ even with us.\nIt is a bit worrisome.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8351284546412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 100.23276559936572
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 105.59943226603242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、帰り道では落ち着いてたんだけどねー\nみんなに迷惑かけたから、ちゃんと謝らなきゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm… I did get her to calm down on the way back‚ though.\nShe wanted to apologize to everyone for all the trouble she caused.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.59943226603244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 109.8660989326991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんだ……すずちゃんって\n少し意地っ張りだけど、根はいい子だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I didn’t know… The thing about Suzu‚\nshe acts tough‚ but she’s a good girl at heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.06609893269908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。それに今日のステージで見せた\nああいう強さはすずだけのもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. And the bold attitude she showed\non stage today is hers alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.66609893269911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 121.93276559936578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "……月ストにはすずの存在が必要だと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest needs Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.93276559936578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 125.48276555168206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.48276555168206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 127.38276555168198
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 127.74943221834867
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "……フン",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Humph!",
        "id": ""
